item.title: Need help
item.dc:creator: @deidera deidera
item.description:
@deidera wrote:

Ok,this could be because if it’s on hamachi,you don’t have it.Or your blocked/the network is invalid.
2-Your firewall/virus scanner/proxy is mistaking a moparscape file on the server malicious and it won’t let you on.
3-Your computer is too old for it to be compatible with moparscape/or the server.Or server contents.
4-The contents of the server are big,lots of people are on,it’s crashing,wait till it gets back online.
5-Your ping isn’t good enought to connect.
6-You don’t have the latest java installed to run MS. ( Moparscape. ).
7-If you do have the latest java,cpnfirm it to your computer.
8-The server’s owner has died in a bloody car crash etc. He’s the only one that knows hpow the server works,it’d offline FOREVER.

Thanks I helped.
